column5: I don't send out alot of PM but I just notice recently when I do, nothing shows up in the send box. Not even sure if the other person got the message. What is wrong?
You have to save it nelly
Nelly...when you compose the message, check a little lower...you have to check the box that says "save to sent box".  You'll be all set then!
Thanks guys, I feel like a fool. Something that is so simple.
